# Semantic token provider

Semantic Token Provider (in addition to TextMate highlighting)

- [ ] Highlight constructor name
- [ ] Highlight parameter names in function expressions
- [ ] Highlight ASDoc tags
- [ ] Highlight import names

# AS3 highlighter

- [x] Directive
- [ ] Expression
  - [x] Comments
  - [x] Variable binding (`var` or `const` followed by pattern) 
  - [ ] Keywords
    - [ ] `null`
    - [ ] `false`
    - [ ] `true`
    - [ ] `this`
    - [ ] `import.meta`
    - [ ] Vector `new <T>`
    - [x] Function `function(...)` or `function name(...)` (here parameters should not be highlighted as parameters, since it may also be a function type)
    - [ ] `new`
    - [ ] `super`
    - [ ] `delete`
    - [ ] `void`
    - [ ] `typeof`
    - [ ] `await`
    - [ ] `yield`
    - [ ] `instanceof`
    - [ ] `in`
    - [ ] `not in`
    - [ ] `is not`
    - [ ] `is`
    - [ ] `as`
    - [ ] `public`
    - [ ] `private`
    - [ ] `protected`
    - [ ] `internal`
  - [ ] Punctuator `::`
  - [ ] Identifier
  - [ ] Numeric literal
  - [ ] Parenthesized `(...)`
  - [ ] String literal
  - [x] Reg exp literal (if either in the beginning of file after any optional whitespace, or preceded by one of (`:`, `=`, `,`, `;`, `(`, `[`, `{`, `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, `%`, `~`, `&`, `^`, `|`, `<`, `>`) possibly between whitespace `\s*`)
  - [x] XML (if either in the beginning of file after any optional whitespace, or preceded by one of (`:`, `=`, `,`, `;`, `(`, `[`, `{`, `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, `%`, `~`, `&`, `^`, `|`, `<`, `>`) possibly between whitespace `\s*`)
  - [x] XML markup (comment, CDATA or processing-instruction)
  - [x] XML list
  - [ ] Semicolon `;`
  - [ ] Square-group `[...]`
  - [ ] Punctuator `...`
  - [ ] Comma `,`
  - [ ] Colon `:`
  - [ ] Object `{ ... }`
    - [ ] Enter context and highlight names more carefully since keywords are allowed 
  - [ ] Apply type or parameterized type `.<...>`
  - [ ] Dot `.` followed by simple identifier
  - [ ] Dot `.`
  - [ ] Attribute `@`
  - [ ] Descendants `..`
  - [ ] Question `?`
  - [ ] Increment `++`
  - [ ] Decrement `--`
  - [ ] Exclamation mark `!`
  - [ ] Plus `+`
  - [ ] Minus `-`
  - [ ] Bitwise not `~`
  - [ ] Power `**`
  - [ ] Times `*`
  - [ ] Divide `/`
  - [ ] Remainder `%`
  - [ ] Shift-left `<<`
  - [ ] Shift-right unsigned `>>>`
  - [ ] Shift-right `>>`
  - [ ] Less-than or equals `<=`
  - [ ] Less-than `<`
  - [ ] Greater-than or equals `>=`
  - [ ] Greater-than `>`
  - [ ] `===`
  - [ ] `==`
  - [ ] `!==`
  - [ ] `!=`
  - [ ] `=`
  - [ ] `&&`
  - [ ] `^^`
  - [ ] `||`
  - [ ] `??`
  - [ ] `&`
  - [ ] `^`
  - [ ] `|`